        protected void onTransform(android.view.View view,

        从类复制的说明: ABaseTransformer
        Called each ABaseTransformer.transformPage(View, float) after ABaseTransformer.onTransform(View, float).
        指定者:
        onTransform 在类中 ABaseTransformer
        参数:
        view - Apply the transformation to this page
        position - Position of page relative to the current front-and-center position of the pager. 0 is front and center. 1 is one full page position to the right, and -1 is one page position to the left.
